# Floating Taco Plugin 
a plugin that works on the following three types of pages on serviceNow 


# "matches" 
https://yum.service-now.com/incident.do* -> incident.js  
https://yum.service-now.com/kb_view.do*  -> kb.js  
https://yum.service-now.com/ui_page.do*  -> landing.js  

https://yum.service-now.com/*nav_to.do*incident.do*
https://yum.service-now.com/*nav_to.do*kb_view.do*
https://yum.service-now.com/*nav_to.do*ui_page.do*

