# Installation Steps: 
1. download the folder and save locally 
2. go to browser extension page: 
    - edge://extensions/
    - chrome://extensions/
3. enable developer mode 
4. unpacked plugin -> choose the plugin folder
5. plugin should auto load on landing page, incident page & KB page 


